init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You open the door and find her sitting at her desk, with a man in a suit sitting across from her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm sorry, but I'm afraid I can't do that." she says in a strained voice.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look at the man, and he smiles at you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Mom, what was that all about?" you ask.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She looks at you, and you see a tear in her eye.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I don't know what to believe anymore.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are still confused, but you know she is telling the truth.
